# The logs/ directory ships EMPTY: this .gitignore keeps the directory
# tracked (git will not store an empty dir) while ignoring every run
# artifact the harness writes here (<GATE>.log, BOARD.md,
# board_status.json). After a workstation run the user force-adds the
# logs for the Architect to audit:
#     git add -f gates/logs
#     git commit -m "workstation board run: logs"
*
!.gitignore
